{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I brought them back to him, and-- but I remember then-- then I also asked somebody else about him, Professor [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know if anybody ever heard of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's one of the foremost authorities on the-- And he knew about him also, so he knows-- knows more about Eastern European people like [INAUDIBLE] He knows more about than what he knew about him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he also said, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's difficult to judge from where we are today whether they were right or wrong what they did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyway, to go back to my story, we-- so he was called to go to-- on a train, which I didn't know at the time was going to Sobibor, together with my aunt and-- and my cousin in 1942.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This must have been in June, July.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think I have the exact date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I gave you the date, I think, when he died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43, Yeah, not '42, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did I say '42?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, '43, it must be '43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was June or July '43, and they were killed in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he had made arrangements for us to stay in an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Westerbork was run in a way-- if you know the story about Thereisenstadt, Terezin, it-- it was in a way similar.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even though it was a transit camp, Theresienstadt also was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were all sort of things going on inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, it was-- For instance, the orphanage was run by a gentleman called Yehoshua Berenbaum with his wife, who had been in Westerbork since 1939.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Westerbork had been established by the Dutch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used it for German refugees who came after the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
